# Sentinel Shield — Semgrep scope for this Laravel + React + Docker example.
# Lives at the repository ROOT; the workflow runs Semgrep with `-w /src` so this is
# honored. SEMGREP / SAST ONLY — does NOT affect composer audit, npm audit, Trivy,
# Syft SBOM, Gitleaks, or Hadolint (they still scan deps/lockfiles/tree/Dockerfile).
# See docs/security/sentinel-shield-adoption.md and the upstream docs/semgrep-scoping.md.

# PHP deps + framework runtime
vendor/
storage/
bootstrap/cache/

# JS toolchain + build output
node_modules/
public/build/
public/hot
dist/
build/
coverage/

# Published / compiled vendor front-end assets (e.g. Filament admin JS) — not source
public/vendor/
public/js/filament/

# The bundled Sentinel Shield checkout is tooling, not application code
tools/sentinel-shield/

# Keep application source scanned: app/, Modules/, resources/js, routes/, config/.
